{"_id": "b16db4e16864361d", "name": "Spacewalk Events", "description":"<h2>Spacewalk Events</h2>", "permission": {"default": 0}, "folder": "", "flags": {"yzecoriolis":{"customJournal":true},"coriolis-ghazali":{"importPath":"Table/Rolltables"}}, "img":"", "results": [{"_id": "cfcd208495d565ef", "type": 0, "weight": 1, "range": [1,2], "text": " <b>EVENT</b>: MUZHADJAR: A pack of muzhadjar have been attracted to the drifting Ghazali and quietly feed near the PCâ€™s path. They scare easily but D6 creatures attack the PC and anyone else nearby. See page 324 in the Coriolis core rulebook for more information. <br/> <b>COST</b>: 1 <br/>" }, {"_id": "c4ca4238a0b92382", "type": 0, "weight": 1, "range": [3,4], "text": " <b>EVENT</b>: LOOSE DEBRIS: Debris breaks off from a damaged part of the hull nearby and drifts toward the PC, who must pass a DEXTERITY test or get hit by a strength 4 attack (weapon damage 1, CRIT 3). <br/> <b>COST</b>: 1 <br/>" }, {"_id": "c81e728d9d4c2f63", "type": 0, "weight": 1, "range": [5,5], "text": " <b>EVENT</b>: GAS LEAK: Corrosive gas bursts forth from a ruptured pipe toward the PC who must pass a DEXTERITY test to avoid getting hit. If this roll is failed, the PC is hit by a strength 3 attack (weapon damage 1, CRIT 1). If the damage sustained is higher than the armor rating of the exo (2 for a normal suit), the suit is compromised and the PC suffers explosive decompression (page 99 of the Coriolis core rulebook). The leaking PC must try to make it to the nearest airlock on her own (DEXTERITY) or get pulled back inside by her comrades using the cable. <br/> <b>COST</b>: 2 <br/>" }, {"_id": "eccbc87e4b5ce2fe", "type": 0, "weight": 1, "range": [6,6], "text": " <b>EVENT</b>: RADIATION BURST: An explosion on the surface of the Hamura star floods the Ghazali in a burst of radiation. Exo suits protect the wearer against normal radiation levels but this is too much. The affected PC suffers D6 points of radiation. <br/> <b>COST</b>: 3 <br/>" }], "replacement": true, "displayRoll": true, "sort": 0, "formula": "d6" }
